data.title: Medicaid and CHIP
data.meta_description: Medicaid and the Children's Health Insurance Program (CHIP) provide health coverage for low-income children, families, seniors and people with disabilities.
data.text:
The .gov means it’s official.

State and federal government websites often end in .gov. Before sharing sensitive information, make sure you’re on an official government site.

The site is secure.

The https:// ensures that you are connecting to the official website and that any information you provide is encrypted and transmitted securely.
